```plantuml
@startuml jes_autopatzer

actor User
participant "React UI (Electron)" as UI
participant "Lichess API" as Lichess
participant "Perl Daemon (autopatzerd)" as Perl
participant "Teensy Controller" as Teensy
participant "Chess Board Hardware" as Hardware

User -> UI : Starts game
UI -> Lichess : Connect via WebSocket
Lichess --> UI : Game events
UI -> Perl : Forward move commands
Perl -> Teensy : Serial command (move piece)
Teensy -> Hardware : Control motors/sensors
Hardware --> Teensy : Position feedback
Teensy --> Perl : Movement confirmation
Perl --> UI : Update status
UI -> Lichess : Send move confirmation
Lichess --> UI : Game state updates
UI -> User : Display updates

@enduml
```